Windows

The below mentioned commands can be used to clear composer cache on windows.

// Check Version
composer --version

// It should show the version like
Composer version 1.5.2 2017-09-11 16:59:25


// Clear the cache
composer clearcache

// It will show the messages as shown below
Clearing cache (cache-vcs-dir): C:\Users\user1\AppData\Local\Composer\vcs
Clearing cache (cache-repo-dir): C:\Users\user1\AppData\Local\Composer\repo
Clearing cache (cache-files-dir): C:\Users\user1\AppData\Local\Composer\files
Clearing cache (cache-dir): C:\Users\user1\AppData\Local\Composer
All caches cleared.
